{"tid":2156009,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"經民聯倡仿內地憑證出入食肆商場  港康碼恐淪電子鐐銬","createTime":"2020-08-14T07:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T07:44:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2379388c3f4de343cbee7666f3a907ad5ead12","tid":2156009,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:20:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/FCMCLQN6OZELPPYRA5JOUXL3CU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FFCMCLQN6OZELPPYRA5JOUXL3CU%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcXPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=fe5b9340\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FFCMCLQN6OZELPPYRA5JOUXL3CU%2F&h=4790a37c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/FCMCLQN6OZELPPYRA5JOUXL3CU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n經民聯倡仿內地憑證出入食肆商場 <br />\n港康碼恐淪電子鐐銬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TCJtrCcA8VyTvKfYFM6l6560JjY=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FQUTNSPZZFEZTDER3KCVLGKOWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTCJtrCcA8VyTvKfYFM6l6560JjY%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFQUTNSPZZFEZTDER3KCVLGKOWM.jpg&h=54b972dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地開發健康碼可追蹤民眾出行，被質疑侵犯人權私隱。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府將推出武肺病毒全民自願檢測計劃，建制派近日力爭香港應仿效內地「健康碼」，規定檢測呈陰性的市民可獲發「港康碼」電子通行證，憑證才可出入食肆、商場等公共地方。人權組織斥港康碼本質上是大型社會監控系統，是另類電子鐐銬，嚴重侵擾港人的人權、自由及私隱。傳染病專家質疑港康碼無助防疫，反或令假陰性病人在社區自由播毒。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：秀茂坪群鼠肉檔爭食 領展令停業<br />\n<br />\n內地健康碼是由支付寶開發的防疫電子通行證，主要下載於手機。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家憂假陰性播疫<br />\n<br />\n建制派各政黨近日多次聯合向政府施壓，要求配合內地支援的全民檢測推出港康碼。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：送亞博者逾半有病徵<br />\n<br />\n內地健康碼向被外國人權組織質疑是另類電子鐐銬。本港民權觀察成員王浩賢指出，所謂港康碼本質上就是一套大型社會監控系統，涉及收集大量個人資料，市民的生活習慣及每日行蹤都可能被監控，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n反對全民檢測的新民主同盟范國威指出，效法內地推行港康碼等如將自願性的全民檢測變成強制性，有港康碼才可外出吃飯購物，亦是限制人身自由。建制派的主張令人懷疑是借防疫之名收集港人DNA資料進行監控，提醒港人切勿上當。<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統科專科醫生梁子超認為，健康碼不應用於開放社區活動，因為病毒潛伏期長達14日，過往亦有不少檢測結果「陰轉陽」的病例，若假陰性病人獲港康碼後以為自己「天下無敵」，到飲食或其他場所周圍走，將造成大型交叉感染，將疫情打回原形。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良亦指港康碼不是好的「解封策略」，只屬經濟安排，擔心會出現不公平情況，僅富有人士有能力付費不斷檢測，才能憑證自由活動。<br />\n<br />\n資料亦顯示，健康碼系統在澳門及浙江均曾發生大型故障，引起民眾不便。而不少內地居民亦投訴健康碼會突然無故變色，令人失去行動自由。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人昨日回應時。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線理事梁啟維亦質疑，港康碼與內地驗測會不會演化成「對政府不滿的人就不能出街？」"},{"pid":"0e7b81ccaa4e65a1edc7b52ac1e17fc2d52a01d5","tid":2156009,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"點都好 返工先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NE8fSJT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNE8fSJT.jpg&h=1d89617e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e45390a8ed810344d9584fa1d5f48d2524904be9","tid":2156009,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e7b81ccaa4e65a1edc7b52ac1e17fc2d52a01d5","tid":2156009,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"點都好 返工先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NE8fSJT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNE8fSJT.jpg&h=1d89617e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"無監控碼 坐唔到車點返工"},{"pid":"4ba861f42eadf79210645de8f7135a3ebe3bce7b","tid":2156009,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e45390a8ed810344d9584fa1d5f48d2524904be9","tid":2156009,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e7b81ccaa4e65a1edc7b52ac1e17fc2d52a01d5","tid":2156009,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"點都好 返工先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NE8fSJT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNE8fSJT.jpg&h=1d89617e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"無監控碼 坐唔到車點返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"為左返工乖乖去驗港康碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0aab05189cc5e17b6aac97ac2a45077ba92051","tid":2156009,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c305a1972fdf7742339ac9a77b651776839120","tid":2156009,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e47ec9ffd3897084d7a54b5390dbaca7a707ab","tid":2156009,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:44:41.000Z","msg":"驗完個碼，都只是代表那一刻是有無事"}]}